Introduction to Cloud Computing - Cloud computing provides services & infrastructure like virtual machines, storage solutions, DBs, networking, IOT, AI & ML over internet rather than relying to physical infrastructure.

Shared Responsibility Model - Saas Paas Iaas

Cloud Models - Private, Public, Hybrid, Multi.
Azure Arc for managing cloud environment.

Azure VMware Solution - for migrating your cloud environment to like public, private or hybrid models.

There are 2 types of expenses to consider
1. Capital Expenditure (CapEx) - It's a one time upfront purchase model, like secure tangible resources (It means these resources are physical assets such as tools, machinery, and building.)
2. Operational expenditure (OpEx) - It works on consumption-based model where basically you pay for the services over time. Cloud falls under this category.
